							<span class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-right">May 2025 — September 2025</span>
						</div>
						<ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
							<li>Developed a Terms & Conditions repository, a central reference tool for credit officers and relationship managers.</li>
							<li>Supported with regular credit analysis and reporting tasks.</li>
