							<span class="text-slate-500 text-sm md:text-right">October 2024 — April 2025</span>
						</div>
						<ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 text-slate-400">
							<li>Enhanced performance monitoring across the commercial credit book through data analysis.</li>
							<li>Produced analysis for test and learn monitoring, leading to policy changes in three major sectors.</li>
							<li>Developed a commercial banking returns dashboard after liaising with stakeholders to identify areas for additional.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
            
          <div class="relative mb-10"> 
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-between md:items-baseline mb-2">
