            <li>Built an indicative credit risk rating tool, reducing time spent and reliance on internal systems for credit analysts.</li>
            <li>Engaged in credit risk monitoring hrough deployment of live dashboards, providing insights into portfolio stability and team capacity.</li>
            <li>Responsible for the oversight and production of MI packs.</li>
