						<a href="https://github.com/jmutale5/hair-type-classification" class="text-blue-400 font-medium hover:underline inline-flex items-center">
							View project on GitHub <span class="ml-1">→</span>
						</a>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all">
						<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
